        <h2><span aria-label="">&#x1F3AF;</span> Focusing on priorities</h2>
        <p>Because our customers' time and energy is valuable, they need the work of HR administration to feel effortless.</dd>
        <h2><span aria-label="">&#x1F320;</span> Shining in moments that matter</h2>
        <p>Because our customers care about their employees, they need help navigating through challenges and seizing opportunities during the entire employee lifecycle.</p>
        <h2><span aria-label="">&#x1F91D;</span> Feeling personally connected</h2>
